title: [SOLVED]820-2936 board battery not charging
message:
this is new board, 820-2936, without battery it run perfect green light , 

it also run with battery , but does not charge the battery , also i if i try charging battery green light  goes off and on , its show the battery parentage on the screen , but does not charge .. 

original isl pin 17 was burnt , i put jumper from pin1 c7050 to isl pin 17,

title: [SOLVED]820-2936 board battery not charging
message: Resistance between 17/18 and 27/28 of the ISL?? Measure on the legs of the chip and not on the cap or probe points

title: [SOLVED]820-2936 board battery not charging
message: Shorted FETs or dead ISL. Replace both and check traces from ISL to FETs.
